---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer style="background: oklch(0.10 0.03 152); border-top: 1px solid oklch(0.22 0.06 152);">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">

    <!-- Top row -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between gap-10 mb-10">

      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="max-w-xs">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-3">
          <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-display font-black text-xs flex-shrink-0"
            style="background: oklch(0.75 0.18 75); color: oklch(0.13 0.04 152);">S</span>
          <span class="font-display font-black text-base" style="color: oklch(0.99 0.004 80);">Somatix</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: oklch(0.48 0.05 152);">
          Tu cuerpo habla. Somatix lo traduce. Calculadora de macros basada en composición corporal real.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-sm">
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold mb-3 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs" style="color: oklch(0.75 0.18 75);">Herramienta</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><a href="#" class="transition-colors duration-150" style="color: oklch(0.50 0.05 152);"
              onmouseenter="this.style.color='oklch(0.78 0.04 152)'"
              onmouseleave="this.style.color='oklch(0.50 0.05 152)'">Calculadora macros</a></li>
            <li><a href="#" class="transition-colors duration-150" style="color: oklch(0.50 0.05 152);"
              onmouseenter="this.style.color='oklch(0.78 0.04 152)'"
              onmouseleave="this.style.color='oklch(0.50 0.05 152)'">Cómo funciona</a></li>
            <li><a href="#" class="transition-colors duration-150" style="color: oklch(0.50 0.05 152);"
              onmouseenter="this.style.color='oklch(0.78 0.04 152)'"
              onmouseleave="this.style.color='oklch(0.50 0.05 152)'">Dispositivos compatibles</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold mb-3 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs" style="color: oklch(0.75 0.18 75);">Empresa</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><a href="#" class="transition-colors duration-150" style="color: oklch(0.50 0.05 152);"
              onmouseenter="this.style.color='oklch(0.78 0.04 152)'"
              onmouseleave="this.style.color='oklch(0.50 0.05 152)'">Política de privacidad</a></li>
            <li><a href="#" class="transition-colors duration-150" style="color: oklch(0.50 0.05 152);"
              onmouseenter="this.style.color='oklch(0.78 0.04 152)'"
              onmouseleave="this.style.color='oklch(0.50 0.05 152)'">Términos de uso</a></li>
            <li><a href="mailto:hola@somatix.app" class="transition-colors duration-150" style="color: oklch(0.50 0.05 152);"
              onmouseenter="this.style.color='oklch(0.78 0.04 152)'"
              onmouseleave="this.style.color='oklch(0.50 0.05 152)'">Contacto</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Bottom bar -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-3 pt-8" style="border-top: 1px solid oklch(0.20 0.05 152);">
      <p class="text-xs" style="color: oklch(0.35 0.04 152);">
        &copy; {year} Somatix. Todos los derechos reservados.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs" style="color: oklch(0.35 0.04 152);">
        Los resultados son orientativos. Consulta con un profesional de la salud ante cualquier duda médica.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</footer>
